            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>οδω καὶ τῇδε <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="2"/>λέσχῃ τερπέσθην κα<supplied reason="lost">ὶ <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="3"/>ἔνθ’ ἀνέμων σκέπας ἦ<supplied reason="lost">ν <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="4"/>πῆξαν τ’ ἀσπασίως <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="5"/>ἀλλ’ ὁ μὲν ἐν πάτρῃ <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="6"/>τῷ δ’ ἔργων πρηκτὴρ <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="7"/>ἀμφὶ δέ μιν πόλεμ<supplied reason="lost">ος <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="8"/>εἰρωτῶν ὃς ἕτλη π<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="9"/>Ἡρώδης Βῆρον κρ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="10"/>πολλῶν καὶ μεγά<supplied reason="lost">λων <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Αὐγούστοις </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>DD</abbr><ex>omini</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ostri</ex></expan> Arcadius <lb n="2"/>et Honorius <lb n="3"/>sub <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> et spe<lb break="no" n="4"/><expan><abbr>ctab</abbr><ex>ili</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>procons</abbr><ex>ule</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Eusebio <lb n="6"/>ϛʹ
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Abweichende Textgestaltung der Z. 7. Die griechische Inschrift stellt ein Herodes Atticus betreffenden Gedicht dar. Sie ist vielleicht auf das Jahr 162 zu datieren. Metrik: elegische Disticha.</p>
